description.en: Our team took the coin when the old developer stopped working on it. In a short time, we fixed a lot of problems and errors in the code and are now updating it. Our goal is to make Azzure as popular as possible. We plan to add new services and list them on exchanges. Due to low fees and fast transactions, Azzure can be used by anyone for exchange and trading. It is a fully decentralized currency. Azzure is actively supported by the community, which is updated with new members every day. We don't make currency for ourselves, we make currency for people, so all improvements and plans are discussed with community members.
